[size=4][u][i][b]  HOW TO INSTALL[/b][/i][/u][/size][size=3]  
[/size]
[size=3]1.Use NMM or extract to your data folder.[/size]
[size=3]2.Go into racemenu with your console  [/size]
[size=3]3.Set race to Nord and go to the presets tab , Press F6 to load the preset.[/size]
[size=3]4.Select the one called "Eve-VarPreset.jslot"[/size]

[i][b][u]PERMISSION[/u]

[b][i][u]HOW TO INSTALL [ BAHASA INDONESIA ]
[/u][/i][/b]
1.Pakai NMM(Nexus Mod Manager) atau Extract dan Simpan di Data Folder Skyrim
2.Buka RaceMenu lewat Console dengan " ` / ~ *
3.Set Ras ke Nord dan Pergi ke tab "Presets" Di atas Kanan Layar,dan tekan tombol F6
4.Pilih file yang bernama "Eve-VarPreset.jslot"
[/size][/center]
